---
title: Mild Thai Green Chicken Curry with Jasmine Rice & Makrut Lime Leaves
description: We’re heating things up by using Thai green curry paste in this creamy sauce, adding a depth and spice that’ll cure any case of tired tastebuds. Balance it out with a bed of jasmine rice and an infusion of citrus with makrut lime leaves to complete this perfect bowl.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mild-thai-green-chicken-curry-ef6b3e36.jpg
